org.openscience.cdk.io.iterator

Interface IIteratingChemObjectReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IChemObjectIO, IChemObjectReader, Iterator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultIteratingChemObjectReader, IteratingMDLReader, IteratingPCCompoundASNReader, IteratingPCCompoundXMLReader, IteratingPCSubstancesXMLReader, IteratingSMILESReader

    public interface IIteratingChemObjectReader
extends IChemObjectReader, Iterator
    Interface for an iterating molecule reader. It allows to iterate over all molecules in specific file format (e.g. SDF), without reading them into memory first. Suitable for very large files, with thousands of molecules.

    Egon Willighagen
